 f(x)=\sum_{k=1}^{\infty}\frac{x^2}{k^2+x^2} 
 |f(x)-f_N(x)|= \left|f(x)-\sum_{k=1}^{N}\frac{x^2}{k^2+x^2}\right|= \left|\sum_{k=N+1}^{\infty}\frac{x^2}{k^2+x^2}\right| 
 \begin{align} \left|\sum_{k=N+1}^{\infty}\frac{x^2}{k^2+x^2}\right| &= \sum_{k=N+1}^{\infty}\frac{x^2}{k^2+x^2}\\ &> \int_{N+1}^\infty \frac{x^2}{k^2+x^2}dk\\ &= x\int_{(N+1)/x}^\infty \frac{1}{1+u^2}du\\ &= x\left(\frac{\pi}{2}-\arctan\left(\frac{N+1}{x}\right)\right) \end{align} 
